	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64195754">The DEC has figured out carry capacities for deer, turkey, black bear, squirrel, and other game populations for all of NY state.  That info plus current population stats is how they determine how many hunting tags to issue each year to hunters.  If they can do it with deer, then other can do it with humans.  Earth's human carrying capacity should be maximized because humans are fricking awesome and there is good reason we are the dominant species.  We are the best hope of all Earth's species to expand life</div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64195754">

